name: Jurgen Mix
description:
This is my first checkpoint model merge, you can try if you want :)

Required Original VAE by Stability AI;

Other Options :

  • Clip skip: 1 or 2

  • ENSD: 31337

  • Eta: 0,68

  • Enable quantization in K samplers

####

"thanks to owner of checkpoint for great work!, source in model versions.

and youtuber Nolan Aatama for Google Colab Stable Diffusion.

We're sending you a virtual high-five and a big thank you for your awesome work! Youre rock!"

####

We're always on the lookout for fresh and exciting works of art, and we know you've got what it takes to blow us away! Post your latest creation in our thread and let's all be inspired.
